Global Gene Synthesis Market Insights
Gene Synthesis Market size was valued at USD 2.8 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 6.8 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 12.2% from 2024 to 2030.

Gene Synthesis Market Overview
The global gene synthesis market is valued at approximately USD 1.7 billion in 2024 and is projected to grow at a compound annual growth rate (CAGR) of 15% over the forecast period (2024-2030). This growth is driven by the increasing demand for gene therapies, personalized medicine, and synthetic biology innovations. The market is expanding as key players enhance their capabilities for high-throughput gene synthesis and streamline processes for custom DNA production. Technological advancements and a rise in the application of gene synthesis in various industries such as pharmaceuticals, agriculture, and diagnostics further contribute to the market's growth.

